76561198319818104,Recommended,253030,29587710,Posted: 30 January,all,kitsune 💜,"Review - Race The Sun""An exciting mini-game that could gob some of your free time.""Race The Sun is a game where you play a solar-powered spacecraft. You'll race from region to region with the setting sun as your timer. Burst through the unique and elegantly made obstacles as you collect energy boosts and other power-ups such as a vertical leap and a speed boosts. As you progress through the levels, you'll unlock upgrades that you can equip to your ship or better yet use a different ship for your high-speed chase for glory.Race The Sun is a decent game but if you're a bit cautious with its price, you can just try to get when it goes on sale. I recommend this game to those who are looking for decent mini-games that are really worth it to burn some of your free time.My Personal Rating:Gameplay: 8/10Music: 7/10Graphics: 7/10Story/Plot: n/aOverall: 7/10"
,Recommended,253030,8032122,"Posted: 13 December, 2013",all,DreaddJester,"To look at this game's store page you'd think, ""looks kinda lame"" however you'd be just as completely and totally WRONG as I was.  First up, and I'm not gonna lie to you here, this game is addictive.  And when I say it's addictive I don't mean, ""oh what a nice little game, I'll play for a few minutes then get on with my day...""  No, it's more like the kind of addiction that grabs you instantly and never lets go.  I'd say it's impossible to play, ""just one round.""  No no.... you'll be like oh man I gotta do that again, I know I can do it better.  Wait wait... I know where I screwed up just one more round.  Oh man, I can't let that stop me.  Just a little more.""But DJ so what if it's addictive it just looks like a silly time waster and I can find those for free.""  Once again your dead wrong.  What the game lacks in graphics it more than double makes up for in gameplay.  It's a racing game that gives you just as much thrills and spills as any racing game out there.  It's a game of dodging stuff that will leave you holding your breath as you narrowly miss that wall with a feeling of relief when you do.  It's a game to challenge you to beat your friends high scores that's just as enjoyable to achieve as the best competitive multiplayer game out there.  It's a game about change as each new day brings a new map to challenge your friends to.  It's a creators paradise where you can create maps and challenges for all your friends and community.  Belive me when I say, this game is a whole lot more than it looks.You honestly can't go wrong adding this gem of a game to your game library.  Buy it when it's cheap, but even at $10.00 I'd still say it's more than worth it.  It'll be your best spent money all week."
