,Recommended,253030,9866773,"Posted: 18 April, 2014",all,Tresky,"Race the Sun is definitely not a new game concept. However, this game takes an existing game concept and amplifies it to be so much better. It you have ever played Cubefield (it's free in-browser, go play it), this game is so much better. You race through a world that changes daily, dodging various obstacles: some that move, some that fall, some that tip over, some that race around, some that go over or under you, etc. The objective is to get as far as you can before the sun goes down or before you crash. The more challenges that you complete in game, the more upgrades you get that allow you to go further and further.Definitely, a game worth trying; especially for a few bucks and to support inide development.9/10"
